summary: Completed comprehensive testing of Journeyman dating app after component refactoring. All 23 backend API tests passed (100%). Frontend UI tests passed - landing page with silhouette backgrounds, login, signup, and navigation all working correctly. The refactored component-based architecture is functioning properly.
passed_tests: Backend API root endpoint (/api/) - returns correct message
User registration (/api/auth/register) - creates user and returns session
Duplicate email registration - correctly rejected with 400
User login (/api/auth/login) - valid credentials work
Invalid login credentials - correctly rejected with 401
Auth me endpoint (/api/auth/me) - returns user with valid token
Auth me without token - correctly returns 401
Logout endpoint (/api/auth/logout) - works correctly
Get profile (/api/profile) - returns user profile
Update profile (/api/profile PUT) - updates bio, profession, age, interests
Complete onboarding (/api/profile/complete-onboarding) - sets onboarding_complete=true
Photo upload (/api/profile/photo) - uploads and counts photos
Discovery endpoint (/api/discover) - returns users list
Discovery with filters (/api/discover?professions=) - filters work
Get matches (/api/matches) - returns matches list
Get likes received (/api/likes-received) - returns likes
Create schedule (/api/schedules POST) - creates travel schedule
Get schedules (/api/schedules GET) - returns user schedules
Delete schedule (/api/schedules/{id} DELETE) - deletes schedule
Get notifications (/api/notifications) - returns notifications
Get unread count (/api/notifications/unread-count) - returns count
Get icebreaker prompts (/api/icebreakers/prompts) - returns prompts list
Activate boost (/api/boost) - activates profile boost
Landing page loads with silhouette background images (3 silhouettes visible)
Landing page has Google signup and Email signup buttons
Login page renders with email/password inputs and Google login option
Signup page renders with name/email/password inputs
Navigation: Landing -> Login works
Navigation: Login -> Signup works
Full signup flow: Form submission -> Dashboard redirect
Session token stored in localStorage after signup
Full login flow: Form submission -> Dashboard redirect
Dashboard page loads for authenticated users
Bottom navigation: Discover, Matches, Chats, Schedules, Profile all work
Swipe action buttons (pass, like, superlike) present on dashboard
critical_code_review_comments: Code architecture is clean - App.js refactored from 1100+ lines to 94 lines with proper component separation
All interactive elements have data-testid attributes for testing
API utility properly uses REACT_APP_BACKEND_URL from environment
AuthContext properly manages user state and session tokens
CSS silhouette animations are well-implemented with subtle breathing effects
test_credentials: Test users created dynamically with unique UUIDs - no persistent test credentials needed
seed_data_creation: No seed data created - tests use dynamically generated test users
context_for_next_testing_agent: All features tested and working. The app has been refactored from monolithic App.js to component-based architecture. Backend has 23 API endpoints all passing. Frontend has proper routing with protected routes. Silhouette background images on landing page are working with dynamic animations.
